txt.en: There is much to be done in the Towers of the Teeth.

Enter the Towers of the Teeth
On your return delve into Carchost, you notice many of the banners put up by the enemy. You decide burning these banners will cause disarray among those devoted to the Dark Lord.
The Towers of the Teeth are located in the Slag-hills.\n\nYou should burn banners in the Towers of the Teeth.
The Towers of the Teeth are located in the Slag-hills.\n\nYou should burn banners in the Towers of the Teeth.
You have burned many banners within the Towers of the Teeth. Your efforts will surely affect the Enemy gathered here.
